    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-05-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-05-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="255"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d255">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Uhl</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Eustis</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-05-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 3, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Waller’s accounts at present suspended. If stepson wishes to come to America, pay
                    his passage upon condition that he reports to the Department upon arrival. If he
                    declines, take his affidavit of facts, providing him temporary maintenance.
                    Caution him to talk with no one.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Uhl</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
